dismissalText.commentary: Ramnaresh Sarwan c Younis Khan b Iftikhar Anjum 49 (65b 9x4 0x6 96m) SR: 75.38

dismissalComment.html: Sarwan falls one short of his fifty, caught at first slip off the outside edge as he played a loose drive to a ball pitched up to him.
